 dark and light themes. Listening for the `dark` class on the `<html />` element and\n  updating the mermaid's theme accordingly\n\n## Install\n\n```sh\nnpm i @theguild/remark-mermaid\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nFollow code will be converted to a mermaid diagram.\n\n````mdx\n// my-page.mdx\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD;\nsubgraph AA [Consumers]\nA[Mobile app];\nB[Web app];\nC[Node.js client];\nend\nsubgraph BB [Services]\nE[REST API];\nF[GraphQL API];\nG[SOAP API];\nend\nZ[GraphQL API];\nA --> Z;\nB --> Z;\nC --> Z;\nZ --> E;\nZ --> F;\nZ --> G;\n```\n````\n","readmeFilename":"README.md"}